    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Asthma subjects:

        Inclusion

          -  Provider diagnosed asthma

          -  FeNO&gt;50 ppb

          -  FEV1 &gt; 1.0 Liter

        Exclusion

          -  COPD by history

          -  Bronchiectasis by history

          -  Pregnant participants

        Normal subjects:

        Inclusion

        - Age matched to asthma subjects

        Exclusion

          -  Any eosinophil disorder by history

          -  Asthma by history

          -  Rhinitis or sinusitis by history
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
